---
// src/pages/solutions/index.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Energy AI Solutions | Amir Aghabiglou">
  <div class="w-full selection:bg-emerald-200 selection:text-emerald-900 py-12">
    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">

      <header class="mb-20 border-b border-slate-200 pb-12">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 border border-emerald-200 text-xs font-bold text-emerald-800 tracking-wide uppercase">
          Domain Expertise // Energy Sector
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-6">
          Intelligent Energy Operations
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
          Translating complex physical data into operational ROI. I bridge the gap between robust statistical analysis and actionable business intelligence for smart grids and sustainable infrastructure.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="mb-24">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

          <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 font-bold text-xl">01</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Smart Grid Fraud Detection</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Non-technical losses (electricity theft) cost utility companies billions annually. Standard detection systems flag anomalies but lack the context required for field action.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              I designed a hybrid system utilizing statistical time-series analysis coupled with an edge-optimized AI reasoning engine. This system not only detects highly complex theft patterns but generates plain-English, interpretable investigation reports for field inspection teams.
            </p>
            <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
              <strong class="block text-sm text-slate-900 mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Business Impact</strong>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                <li>&bull; Actionable, explainable AI (SHAP integration)</li>
                <li>&bull; Edge-deployable to reduce cloud compute costs</li>
                <li>&bull; Drastic reduction in false-positive field dispatches</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 font-bold text-xl">02</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Building Energy Profiling</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Optimizing HVAC heating and cooling loads requires precise calculation of a building's physical dimensions, orientation, and glazing area.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              I engineered a dual-brained advisory tool that calculates exact energy footprints using robust numerical regression. It then translates those raw engineering metrics into practical, human-readable recommendations (e.g., "Reduce glazing area to 15% to cut cooling loads by 10%").
            </p>
            <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
              <strong class="block text-sm text-slate-900 mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Business Impact</strong>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                <li>&bull; Instant, automated energy auditing</li>
                <li>&bull; Zero AI hallucination via strict schema enforcement</li>
                <li>&bull; Direct translation of physical specs to HVAC costs</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-16 text-center text-white shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to optimize your energy infrastructure?</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 text-lg">
          Whether you need to detect anomalies in terabyte-scale smart grid data or require a predictive model for infrastructure efficiency, I build reliable systems that deliver measurable outcomes.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-emerald-500 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-emerald-400 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/30">
          Initiate a Consultation
        </a>
      </section>

    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>